can be used for pull requests in\nthe Bears repository. We present in this paper the approach employed by Bears,\nand we deliver the version 1.0 of Bears, which contains 251 reproducible bugs\ncollected from 72 projects that use the Travis CI and Maven build environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 22:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-04"}
