 the gas composition. A mechanism involving the heating of the\ncathode surface as trigger for secondary discharges is proposed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 23:29:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 14:21:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-28"}
