e that of continuous\nPoisson capacity channel linearly increases. The above theoretical results are\nextensively validated by numerical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jan 2019 13:21:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 16:01:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-15"}
